        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4015555930" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12616254489722250715">Thoroughly enjoyed this authorised sequel to The Time Machine. Stephen Baxter really captured the original feel while also pulling in today&apos;s science into the mix. Some of this was way beyond me, but it didn&apos;t spoil the time I had. Really glad I read this one. Loved the different take on the Morlocks.<br/><br/>Solid 4 stars.</span>
  <span id="freeText12616254489722250715" style="display:none">Thoroughly enjoyed this authorised sequel to The Time Machine. Stephen Baxter really captured the original feel while also pulling in today's science into the mix. Some of this was way beyond me, but it didn't spoil the time I had. Really glad I read this one. Loved the different take on the Morlocks.<br /><br />Solid 4 stars.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12616254489722250715" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

